{"tid":587844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國跨光譜議員NGO　發30頁報告　要求取消311補選　立即恢復DQ議員議席　議員被DQ屬非法","createTime":"2018-03-10T17:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T13:18:18.000Z","uid":47714,"like":138,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"832bac7acdf491fac6018d9d064e552a5f2a9125","tid":587844,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:32:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/03/311-hk-watch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2018%2F03%2F311-hk-watch%2F&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=fbb3d152\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2018/03/311-hk-watch/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/58ecfa82e3df284d3a13dd41/t/5aa101644192022702931c8f/1520501099097/PS.png?format=500w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F58ecfa82e3df284d3a13dd41%2Ft%2F5aa101644192022702931c8f%2F1520501099097%2FPS.png%3Fformat%3D500w&h=00b4da49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三一一補選前三日，英倫人權組織Hong Kong WATCH發表報告，要求取消補選，恢復被人DQ議員的議席，事關今次補選經已因為DQ參選人及議員而蒙污! 報告強調參選人受政治篩選，中國政府干預香港選舉，蠶食香港自治。報告要求國際社會緊急關注，尤其是中英聯合聲明簽署國英國。<br />\n<br />\n前英國外相兼香港監察贊助人MALCOLM RIFKIND爵士兼御用大律師在報告序中曰：這份報告顯示中國政府九七年所接受的義務受到侵蝕，令人不安。DQ參選人的做法令人倍加擔心當局早有預謀，要逐步減少香港自治。<br />\n<br />\n報告：<a href=\"https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2018/3/7/political-screening-and-the-erosion-of-autonomy-new-hong-kong-watch-report-questions-tainted-by-elections\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongwatch.org%2Fall-posts%2F2018%2F3%2F7%2Fpolitical-screening-and-the-erosion-of-autonomy-new-hong-kong-watch-report-questions-tainted-by-elections&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=478f24af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongwatch.org/all-posts/2018/3/7/political-screening-and-the-erosion-of-autonomy-new-hong-kong-watch-report-questions-tainted-by-elections</a><br />\n<br />\ncancelling the by-elections on 11 March 2018, and immediately reinstating all<br />\nillegally disqualified lawmakers"},{"pid":"a10bf65dd0cc7a37a01ee3f3849350753c3c60fa","tid":587844,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7b1b0718ff8f12304ea9fc9d68ded132a34b51","tid":587844,"uid":17510,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:44:17.000Z","msg":"終於講返句人話"},{"pid":"3b42c6dabe58572dfbba5ed686927171eebf94bb","tid":587844,"uid":55488,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:46:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ef41497d4dafd62f6b8e312168b81a4bf30ad94","tid":587844,"uid":31920,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n靠你勇武做實事表演啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4776d0b252dcab7cf9b97678d9b8c63a805b037e","tid":587844,"uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T18:00:30.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jeffreytnau/posts/10157375049148298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjeffreytnau%2Fposts%2F10157375049148298&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7b700b7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jeffreytnau/posts/10157375049148298</a>[/url]<br />\n<br />\n其實其他制度也是會製造公意承認的合法地位，例如說自己是天意、天命、神授，例如中共說中國只能由他們領導。秩序的建立，是需要當中的人服從，維持成本才會低，沒有了一堆人自動服從，不但弱勢，還會無法少數統治多數。<br />\n<br />\n民主與它們不同，不但在於這是必需，還在於只能透過各種形式，由承受秩序的當事人表態意願，去將政權認受和合法化，否則就是非法。民主是不可能自己製造這種公受性的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TaiwaneseLocalismFront/posts/550188008675642\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTaiwaneseLocalismFront%2Fposts%2F550188008675642&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c67da111\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TaiwaneseLocalismFront/posts/550188008675642</a><br />\n<br />\n‧英國。英國不但是香港的中英聯合聲明簽署國，而且英國一直有一種說法，就是，對香港人有道義責任。香港出現了甚麼有關政治前景的事，都容易出現在英國媒體的國際新聞，亦即容易出現在國際社會。英國將來要做甚麼，透過香港，也是名正言順的。"},{"pid":"2a68d84df56755787d1f6bda9ce9d957371a81fb","tid":587844,"uid":93986,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T18:01:24.000Z","msg":"香港狗要前主人發聲<br />\n但自己就要同現主人搖尾乞憐"},{"pid":"388940622aa5c641b06da5594710a4624a3e21b5","tid":587844,"uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.wenxuecity.com/news/2016/11/04/5741770_print.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wenxuecity.com%2Fnews%2F2016%2F11%2F04%2F5741770_print.html&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=fe78f243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wenxuecity.com/news/2016/11/04/5741770_print.html</a><br />\n<br />\n這支民團將自己命名為「百份之三」，他們解釋道在美國獨立戰爭期間，上陣殺敵的美國人佔到當時人口的3%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152968050912357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10152968050912357&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=e28d1163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10152968050912357</a><br />\n<br />\n搞美國獨立, 但是北美當時還有三份之二的人是保皇黨或者「唔想搞咁多野」者"},{"pid":"2d638a56bb2b62842ad0f7927822db8bbaa76db6","tid":587844,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T18:47:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chenglap-ptt.blogspot.hk/2010/07/re_179.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchenglap-ptt.blogspot.hk%2F2010%2F07%2Fre_179.html&d=f523n4gChKvkFqIVfjeVmp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9ca6d97c\" target=\"_blank\">http://chenglap-ptt.blogspot.hk/2010/07/re_179.html</a><br />\n<br />\n推 a1282:不用別人幫忙？不用別人幫忙推翻的了本地的政府嗎？ 07/02 22:05<br />\n<br />\n國際勢力是戰略問題.<br />\n民主是制度問題.<br />\n<br />\n兩件事其實毫無關係, 比方說, 你要打仗, 附近有一支外國軍隊肯有<br />\n條件地幫你, 你引他進來就能打贏這場仗, 就是「引外國來干涉」,<br />\n但戰略上你應該這樣做就是.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&rarr; a1282:孫文沒有日本暗助，讓他購買武器，怎麼搞革命？ 07/02 22:06<br />\n&rarr; a1282:理論上如c大所言沒錯，可實際操作上往往不是如此 07/02 22:06<br />\n<br />\n現實是, 外國不只一個, 而是很多個, 外國之間的利益也互相衝突.<br />\n以中華民國為例, 先後受過日本, 蘇聯, 德國, 美國的影響, 但也同<br />\n時跟其中兩個宣戰過. 跟蘇聯敵對過."},{"pid":"5097623139f62723cae65db0bc50bf02b8fe914f","tid":587844,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8cd6be565ea8338505718b27bd79430c49a655","tid":587844,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9e6102aa6d5535f70c3146d1088f470a596ae1","tid":587844,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:08:45.000Z","msg":"大地在我腳下"},{"pid":"30fd89026f71e4e2893718995a35d5986b8d2900","tid":587844,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4683c5a68e0cebd01b55e88dce673836f313c9f0","tid":587844,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:13:48.000Z","msg":"咁撚深奧<br />\n香港狗唔會明"},{"pid":"068a3d02888528c0ee463f4b6026941f2326fda8","tid":587844,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4683c5a68e0cebd01b55e88dce673836f313c9f0","tid":587844,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:13:48.000Z","msg